title: Milavice
text:
Milavice is a <a href="village">village</a> in the <a href="Municipalities%20of%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina">municipality</a> of <a href="Busova%C4%8Da">Busovača</a>, <a href="Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina">Bosnia and Herzegovina</a>.
Demographics.
According to the 2013 census, its population was 105.
